==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A [[participant]] (fighter) in a [[boxing]] match.
# A [[breed]] of [[stocky]], [[medium-sized]], [[short-haired]] dog with a [[square-jawed]] [[muzzle]].
# Chinese anti-imperial and anti-foreigner rebels in early 1900s.
# {{two-up}} The person running the game.

====Synonyms====
